  stimulus_text = 'The author explores the relationship between the human experience of smell and the way that humans perceive other people. The author points out that, for many people, the experience of smell is closely linked to the experience of memory, and the author suggests that these experiences can have a profound impact on a person''s relationships. How is the human experience of smell used to illustrate a larger idea?',
